conjecture(weak-pfr-symm): weak Polynomial Freiman-Ruzsa, the entropy route

A set with small doubling is efficiently covered by a coset of a subgroup. PFR's
weak / entropic form, the WeakPFR strand of teorth/pfr.

Status: math.conjectured
