formalize(entropy-basic): Shannon entropy and its basic inequalities

Status: math.machine-checked
---
formalize(ruzsa-distance): the entropic Ruzsa distance and its triangle inequality

Status: math.machine-checked
Depends-On: entropy-basic
---
formalize(tau-functional): the tau-functional and its minimiser

Status: math.machine-checked
Depends-On: ruzsa-distance
---
formalize(pfr-projection): the projection lemma onto a finite-index subgroup

Status: math.machine-checked
Depends-On: ruzsa-distance
---
formalize(app-ent-pfr): the approximate-entropy PFR inequality

The proof unfolds the tau-functional minimiser's definition body.

Status: math.machine-checked
Depends-On: tau-functional
---
formalize(torsion-dist-shrinking): Ruzsa distance shrinks under the torsion quotient

Status: math.machine-checked
Depends-On: app-ent-pfr
---
formalize(torsion-free-doubling): the torsion-free doubling bound

Status: math.machine-checked
Depends-On: torsion-dist-shrinking, pfr-projection
---
formalize(weak-pfr-asymm): the asymmetric weak PFR

Status: math.machine-checked
