fix(app-ent-pfr)!: adopt the module system (v4.28-rc1, same Mathlib) -- silent sorryAx

The proof unfolds a definition body the module system now leaves unexposed across
the public-import boundary, so it silently elaborates to sorryAx. lake build still
succeeds; an out-of-module #print axioms shows the hole. No literal token in source.

Status: math.open
BREAKING CHANGE: app-ent-pfr rests on sorryAx behind green CI.
